$ advanced-validation

  advanced-validation is an example showcasing Click's built-in
  parameter validation and constraint mechanisms.

  This example requires Click 8.3 or higher with the new
  validation features.

Features demonstrated:
  - Range validation (min_val, max_val, min_open, max_open)
  - Regex/pattern validation
  - Parameter dependencies (requires)
  - Mutual exclusivity (exclusive_with)
  - Validation callbacks
  - Help display with validation hints

Usage:

  $ pip install --editable .
  $ advanced-validation --help
